page.title: 10Wildlife at Newmillerdam
page.content: The following is a catalogue of wildlife at Newmillerdam Country Park. Birds Animals Fish Reed Bunting Grey Squirrel Pike Sedge Warbler Badger Bream Mallard Mink* Tench Moorhen Hedgehog Roach Teal Rabbit Perch Tufted Duck Shoveller Coot Gt.Crested Grebe Goosander Owls* * The mink are few in number and have obviously found their way to the Park after escaping from mink farms. The owls are introduced to the woodland by the Royal Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals after being found injured in the Wakefield area.
